{"image_id": "ISRG_2010_page_72", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Table of Contents", "bbox": [75.0, 107.5, 193.9, 123.3]}, {"text": "Recent Accounting Pronouncements", "bbox": [75.0, 149.0, 354.9, 169.7]}, {"text": "Adopted Accounting Pronouncements", "bbox": [75.0, 178.9, 352.0, 199.4]}, {"text": "In September 2009, the Financial Accounting Standards Board (“FASB”) amended the accounting standards related to revenue recognition for", "bbox": [118.8, 209.4, 1113.3, 228.9]}, {"text": "arrangements with multiple deliverables and arrangements that include software elements (“new accounting principles”). The new accounting principles permit", "bbox": [75.0, 231.3, 1183.9, 250.7]}, {"text": "prospective or retrospective adoption, and the Company elected prospective adoption at the beginning of the first quarter of 2010. See “Revenue Recognition”", "bbox": [75.0, 253.4, 1163.5, 272.6]}, {"text": "section above for more details on the related accounting.", "bbox": [75.0, 275.3, 462.6, 294.5]}, {"text": "Effective January 1, 2010, the Company adopted revised guidance intended to improve disclosures related to fair value measurements, issued by FASB.", "bbox": [118.8, 312.5, 1187.2, 332.1]}, {"text": "This guidance requires the Company to separate information about significant transfers in and out of Level 1 and Level 2 and the reason for such transfers,", "bbox": [75.0, 334.3, 1168.1, 354.0]}, {"text": "and also requires information related to purchases, sales, issuances, and settlements information of Level 3 financial assets to be included in the rollforward of", "bbox": [75.0, 356.2, 1186.7, 375.9]}, {"text": "activity. The guidance also requires the Company to provide certain disaggregated information on the fair value of financial assets and requires disclosure on", "bbox": [75.0, 378.2, 1172.6, 397.7]}, {"text": "valuation techniques and inputs used for both recurring and nonrecurring fair value measurements of Level 2 and Level 3 financial assets. The Company’s", "bbox": [75.0, 400.0, 1164.7, 419.6]}, {"text": "policy is to recognize transfers into or out of levels as of the actual date of the event or change in circumstances that caused the transfer.", "bbox": [75.0, 422.1, 1018.6, 441.5]}, {"text": "NOTE 3. CASH, CASH EQUIVALENTS & INVESTMENTS", "bbox": [75.0, 468.2, 553.5, 488.5]}, {"text": "The following tables summarize the Company’s cash, cash equivalents and investments as of December 31, 2010 and 2009 (in millions):", "bbox": [118.8, 498.4, 1085.8, 518.1]}, {"text": "Amortized", "bbox": [764.4, 558.0, 820.2, 571.7]}, {"text": "Cost", "bbox": [780.0, 573.2, 804.8, 587.4]}, {"text": "Gross", "bbox": [897.3, 542.1, 928.5, 556.1]}, {"text": "Unrealized", "bbox": [886.3, 558.5, 940.8, 571.5]}, {"text": "Gains", "bbox": [898.8, 574.0, 928.3, 587.2]}, {"text": "Gross", "bbox": [1011.4, 542.1, 1042.6, 556.1]}, {"text": "Unrealized", "bbox": [1000.5, 558.5, 1054.9, 571.5]}, {"text": "Losses", "bbox": [1009.8, 571.9, 1070.0, 589.2]}, {"text": "Fair Value", "bbox": [1122.4, 571.9, 1190.4, 589.2]}, {"text": "December 31, 2010", "bbox": [75.0, 588.9, 219.5, 608.8]}, {"text": "Cash and cash equivalents:", "bbox": [75.0, 610.7, 268.8, 630.8]}, {"text": "Cash", "bbox": [120.3, 632.0, 157.6, 652.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [759.7, 632.0, 769.0, 652.8]}, {"text": "20.1", "bbox": [795.7, 632.0, 845.6, 654.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [886.3, 632.0, 895.6, 652.8]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [912.9, 632.0, 959.8, 654.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1000.5, 632.0, 1009.8, 652.8]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [1027.0, 632.0, 1070.0, 654.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1116.1, 632.0, 1125.5, 652.8]}, {"text": "20.1", "bbox": [1155.2, 632.0, 1195.8, 652.8]}, {"text": "Cash equivalents", "bbox": [120.3, 654.6, 241.3, 674.5]}, {"text": "259.7", "bbox": [781.6, 653.9, 845.6, 676.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [912.9, 653.9, 959.8, 676.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [1027.0, 653.9, 1070.0, 676.7]}, {"text": "259.7", "bbox": [1141.2, 653.9, 1195.8, 674.7]}, {"tex